post_text:
Good afternoon, all!

We will be asking for students to turn in their laptops this week! All assignments and grades are due by Wednesday, May 20th. We need to recollect all technology to ensure we have enough inventory for next year.

Junior High students:
Please plan on returning your laptops and chargers to NFL Yet High campus (222 E Olympic Drive) Tuesday or Wednesday, May 19th-20th, between 8 am-12 pm.

High school students:
Please plan on returning your laptops and chargers to NFL Yet High campus (222 E Olympic Dr) Next Thursday or Friday, May 21st-22nd, between 8 am-12 pm.

The NFL Yet High office will have very limited office hours (8am-12 pm), and we will practice safe measures. If you need to call, admin and front office staff will be present to assist during those times. Thank you!

post_text: Today we celebrated our Class of 2018 Success at our first ever College Signing Day.
